## Context

The Transformers.js library already defines `AutoModelForImageTextToText` in `src/models.js` (line 8736) with support for LLaVA, Florence-2, Moondream, Qwen2-VL, Idefics3, SmolVLM, PaliGemma, and more — but there is no corresponding high-level pipeline. This change adds an `ImageTextToTextPipeline` class so users can do:

```js
